author: Bakari Tice | btice@njadvancemedia.com
title: Boys indoor track Fab 50, Jan. 16: Strong individual performances leads to movement
text:
The indoor track season has reached its midpoint with teams competing for state relay titles at the NJSIAA Relay Championships this week.
With the action just getting underway, its time to highlight the the top athletes once again with the release of the latest boys Fab 50, set to rank the top 50 athletes in the state regardless of event. Despite all eyes being on the relay championships, strong individual performances from last week should lead to some movement in the rankings.
